 The horsmen except for death cuz he is off ona mission ran to drillbit's 
aid. Sphink also appeared in the sound of fire. He knew of Kit Kat's death 
and of course sided with her sucsessor. Sphink injected drill bit in the arm 
with some healing fluid. "This will counter the venom that entered your 
system. Now let apocalypse finish him off. Quick strike is no match for him 
in his present state. They watched as apocalypse's blade came down and waited 
to see what happened.
